                <img src="images/Enemies/43f178fc49c2ce0a961eba98af0ffda69996e80e.png" alt="Devastator">
            </div>
            <div class="ec-text">
                <h3>Devastator</h3>
                <p>The ironclad Devastator seeks to crush opponents of the Automatons' totalitarian worldview with a diverse array of heinous weaponry: arm-cannons, arm-shields, arm-machineguns and arm-rocket-launchers.</p>
                <div class="table-container">
                        <table>
                            <tr>
                                <th>Stats</th>
                                <th>Values</th>
                                <th>Action</th>
                                <th>Damage</th>
                                <th>Hit-mod</th>
                            </tr>
    
                            <tr>
                                <td>AC</td>
                                <td>14</td>
                                <td>F-Assault Cannon</td>
                                <td><span class="dice">2d8</span><br>Plasma</td>
                                <td>+2</td>
                            </tr>
    
                            <tr>
                                <td>HP</td>
                                <td>33</td>
                                <td>Reinforced Steel Fist</td>
                                <td><span class="dice">1d12</span><br>Impact</td>
                                <td>+2</td>
                            </tr>
    
